The paper discusses the application of machine learning and predictive analytics, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also addresses societal challenges, which could fall under the categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The use of data and information for decision-making could also fall under the category of cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper discusses case studies, which could fall under the category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
